Our beautiful journey of creating @thechungmanali 💗

This is what we mean when we say we have put our hearts into creating The Chung 💗
It was a childhood dream that finally became a reality.
Yes it was tough, it was tiring and sometimes it was emotional but at the end it doesn’t matter when you see what you’ve done you feel proud and happy 🥹
Thank you everybody who helped us make this possible 🤍
We welcome you to be a part of our dream and have the best time of your life 💗

Follow for more and DM for bookings 🌸

.

Welcome to The Chung 💗

A modern 5-bedroom villa, conveniently located near the highway yet tucked away in a peaceful setting with a spacious garden and ample drive-in parking. The entire property is securely fenced for your peace of mind.

Manali is just a 30-minute drive (18 kilometers) away, while Naggar Castle is a short 15-minute ride (4.5 kilometers) from our doorstep. Inside, you’ll find a well-equipped kitchen, a comfortable living area, a bonfire spot, and a serene pond.

Experience comfort and convenience in our cozy villa – your ideal retreat.
We are now OPEN FOR BOOKINGS 💗
